com.i2group.apollo.alertretrievalservice.transport

Class Alert

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.alertretrievalservice.transport.Alert
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RepositoryAlert

    public abstract class Alert
extends Object
    An alert, as generated by an alert feed in response to a change to an item in the Analysis Repository.

      • Alert

        protected Alert(ItemIdentifier feedIdentifier,
                ItemIdentifier subjectIdentifier,
                String alertType,
                PropertyValue timestamp)
        Constructs a new Alert, initializing all mandatory fields.
        Parameters:
        feedIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the alert feed that generated this Alert.
        subjectIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the Item that changed in order to cause this Alert.
        alertType - A String containing the type of the Alert, as returned by getAlertType().
        timestamp - A PropertyValue containing the timestamp of the Alert.
